{"id":288560,"date":[{"year":1953,"month":7,"day":3}],"page":"8","source":"“少年先锋队”","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"文化广场","column":"","genre":"","count":"420","ytitle":"","mtitle":"对坏学生的批评","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入3号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1953\\07\\5373080101.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>吴晔</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>一、轻信的祖母"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你又上那儿去，孩子?”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“啊，亲爱的祖母，到小组去!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是晚会，就是会议，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是读报，就是小队会……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万良叹了一口气说道:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接着就跑了，——到电影院。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入3号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1953\\07\\5373080102.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>二、万良在准备考试"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万良的情景是悲哀的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可怜的他混身发抖:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他藏匿了近百张的“夹带”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把它放在皮鞋里或口袋中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是他不知道——这就是不幸!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反正什么地方也不能隐藏!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入3号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1953\\07\\5373080103.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>三、聪明的打算"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我何必自己来加、减、乘、除呢?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反正有个优等生在我的近旁!……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是在生活中遇到更复杂的问题时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必须要自己用脑子啊!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入3号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1953\\07\\5373080104.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>四、他和书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是什么?请告诉我!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这本可怜的书那里去了?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么封面和封底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都不见了?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于这个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请问这位勇士吧!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入3号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1953\\07\\5373080105.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>五、魔术的转变"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万良就这样:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏着自行车飞驶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“天啊，真痛快!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是在学习的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是愁眉不展就是打瞌睡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你还认得他吗?</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入3号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1953\\07\\5373080106.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>六、他为什么学习?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“爸爸，我要买冰鞋、买球；”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当爸爸买回礼物的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“噢，爸爸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我并不是为了这一些些东西才念书的!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(原载“少年先锋队”杂志，吴晔　改写。)</FONT>"}]}